The '''Third Deep''' was a level in [[Moria|Khazad-dûm]] that had treasuries and armories. It was below the [[Great Gates|East Gate]] of Moria. During [[Balin]]'s short [[Balin's Colony|recolonization]] of Moria, he sent [[Óin]] to find an access to it.<ref>{{FR|II5}}</ref>
